try to understand more about

00:10:48.190 --> 00:10:50.980 align:middle line:84%
how it is that you do the
wonderful work that you do.

00:10:50.980 --> 00:10:54.252 align:middle line:84%
Because I understand,
on several levels,

00:10:54.252 --> 00:10:56.710 align:middle line:84%
