in terms of your vision loss.

00:10:56.710 --> 00:10:59.260 align:middle line:84%
Yet, you've been able
to do remarkable things

00:10:59.260 --> 00:11:01.840 align:middle line:84%
beyond what most
artists can do, even

00:11:01.840 --> 00:11:03.238 align:middle line:90%
