mindfulness that

00:11:47.610 --> 00:11:53.850 align:middle line:84%
are helping us learn how
to pursue our specialties,

00:11:53.850 --> 00:11:56.680 align:middle line:84%
and to develop our resilience
and our mindfulness.

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:59.230 align:middle line:84%
And so I think this is
a very important topic.

00:11:59.230 --> 00:12:01.320 align:middle line:84%
It's something that is
actually quite ancient,

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:04.620 align:middle line:84%
and that we're just tapping back
into an understanding of what

00:12:04.620 --> 00:12:07.740 align:middle line:84%
this means, for how to
be successful in the face

00:12:07.740 --> 00:12:09.070 align:middle line:90%
of adversity.

00:12:09.070 --> 00:12:11.070 align:middle line:84%
I think you really are
an inspiration to us all,

00:12:11.070 --> 00:12:13.200 align:middle line:84%
and to many of my
own patients, who

00:12:13.200 --> 00:12:15.330 align:middle line:84%
