deal with for your life.

00:12:18.780 --> 00:12:21.036 align:middle line:90%
It's my honor to be your doctor.

00:12:21.036 --> 00:12:21.972 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, thanks.

00:12:21.972 --> 00:12:27.130 align:middle line:90%


00:12:27.130 --> 00:12:30.950 align:middle line:84%
>> Perseverance is just moving
forward even when it gets

00:12:30.950 --> 00:12:31.750 align:middle line:90%
