00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:04.260 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, well, that's not
what I want to be known for.

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:05.790 align:middle line:84%
I want to be known
as a good artist.

00:13:05.790 --> 00:13:09.248 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:13:09.248 --> 00:13:14.690 align:middle line:90%


00:13:14.690 --> 00:13:16.220 align:middle line:84%
Even when I was
younger, I always

00:13:16.220 --> 00:13:20.660 align:middle line:84%
